Why Every Woman Needs Thought Leadership, Not Just Content
https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/brand-brunch-issue-01-why-every-woman-needs-thought-just-ekezie-kncme

We’re in a digital world where everyone is posting but only a few are influencing how people think, feel, and choose.

That’s what thought leadership does. And if you’re a woman building anything, a brand, a business, a legacy , you need it.

Because here’s the truth: Content makes noise. Thought leadership makes moves.
